Perak Mufti Tan Sri Harussani Zakaria said women should never say no to their husbands . 
  He said the Prophet Mohammed said a wife can only refuse if she is pregnant or sick . 
  He also said a woman can only say no if they are on the back of a camel . 
  Said the idea of marital rape was 'made up by European people' His fatwa has horrified many in Malaysia and beyond . 
 